{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ddaf5904bc","title":"关于高凌云师与陕北伊盟部队合编的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"150e462510","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":19,"articleId":"ddaf5904bc"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"dbc22ee46c","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高凌云，当时任中国人民解放军西北军区独立第二师师长。"},{"id":"bbde6ef763","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀，当时任中共中央西北局第一书记、中国人民解放军第一野战军司令员兼政治委员。习，指习仲勋，当时任中共中央西北局书记、中国人民解放军西北军区政治委员。"},{"id":"d8a9b97971","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"习，指习仲勋。张，指张宗逊，当时任中国人民解放军第一野战军第一副司令员。14]左协中，原国民党政府军将领，1948年5月率部在陕西榆林地区起义。"}],"contents":[{"id":"18d21ddc2d","type":"title","text":"关于高凌云“师与陕北伊盟部队合编的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc"},{"id":"dbc22ee46c","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、习","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc"},{"id":"bbde6ef763","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为习、张问西灰电第二方案较好。高凌云仍当第二师师长。该师开回陕北与陕北伊盟部合编，加强战力，作为陕北伊盟警备部队，如此对外影响较好。左协中“在政协会后有进步，应在陕西给以适当位置（例如省府委员）。以上请的定。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc"},{"id":"d8a9b97971","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc"},{"id":"da9d860571","type":"subtitle","text":"西皓","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc"}],"page":{"id":"2ec739024d","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"ddaf5904bc